{"about_the_game":"<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/Logo_2.png?t=1719403126\" /><br><br>Outpost brings the perfect mix between survival and roguelite gameplay. Start the game in a randomly generated environment and try to make it through as many nights as possible. How long can you survive? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/H_Seasons.png?t=1719403126\" /><br>Each playthrough starts in a different season, forcing you to <strong>adapt</strong> even more. Spend you time wisely during the short winter days, or go the extra mile during summer!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/Snowman.png?t=1719403126\" /><br><br>As the game progresses, you will unlock extra features for each of the <strong>four seasons</strong>. Every season has its own set of features, so you'll have to rethink your strategy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/Springvine.png?t=1719403126\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/H_Gear_Up.png?t=1719403126\" /><br>Every time you finish a playthrough, you gain experience that can be spent on upgrading your survival talents. Strategically choose your next move from <strong>100+ upgrades</strong>.<br><br>You'll also receive new <strong>items to wield</strong>, granting you extra bonuses and stats. <strong>Create your perfect set of gear</strong>, tailored to your favorite strategy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/Items.png?t=1719403126\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/H_Base.png?t=1719403126\" /><br>Defending your base can be done in different ways. <strong>Gather resources</strong> and create static defenses such as <strong>Turrets and Campfires</strong>, <strong>Cannons and Magic Crystals</strong> or even <strong>Snowman Cannons</strong> (what?!). You can also craft yourself a bow and<strong> join the fight yourself.</strong><br>With every season having different features, you'll have to figure out the best plan for each playthough!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/Base.png?t=1719403126\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1127110/extras/H_Leaderboards.png?t=1719403126\" /><br>Everyone is competing to become the best. Are you capable of beating all your friends? Perhaps you even have a secret strategy that allows you to become <strong>Number 1</strong> on the <strong>Global Leaderboards</strong>!<br><br>Also check out our newest upcoming release, Spellsinger Towns!<br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"All Nighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/933349475dc57f7c6fdb6465499486951bf99fdb.jpg"},{"name":"(no) Night's sleep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/331ed111a87fdd2845ef10c9e31b67c296e8bda8.jpg"},{"name":"Nights of Cydonia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/abd7a6ca10b7e0129bdaa692b630ae0526095b4b.jpg"},{"name":"Dark and full of terrors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/5020ba6fdfdb0d38b09f97b08ea0157ebe44a86c.jpg"},{"name":"Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/bfba09c97bb91ba08a392fa014219c761c6c338c.jpg"},{"name":"Student","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1127110/3b9fa368